               <msContents class="#MTM">
                  <summary>A multiple-text manuscript containing two Dharmaśāstra works copied for Ducler in 1830-1831 by Śorakkuḍi [Tamil Curakkuṭi] Kṛṣṇaśasāstrin. It contains: 
<list rend="numbered">
  <item>an incomplete Mitāksarā (Adhyāya 2 only, that is the Vyavahārādhyāya) (U1)</item>
  <item>the Vyavahāranirṇaya by Varadarāja (U3, f155v), apparently preceded by an unidentified work (U3, f149r)</item>
  </list></summary>
                  
